casebody.data:
James Franklin McCLELLAND
v.
NORTH CAROLINA INDUSTRIAL COMMISSION, et al. No. 479P04-3. Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 14, 2005. James Franklin McClelland, pro se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 9th day of September 2005 in this matter for a writ of mandamus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in Conference this the 14th day of September 2005."
